paragraphs: Hello! I am currently a Senior at the University of Michigan Ann Arbor majoring in Industrial & Operations Engineering with a minor in Complex Systems. I hail from the Seattle region but have been fortunate to travel the world and aim to work in an international setting. I have a background in Energy and Sustainability research with technical experience in software development and data analysis. I am fascinated by a host of topics and extremely eager to apply sustainability practices in research/business environments. Attached below is my resume but please feel free to reach out with any questions through the email icon on the top!
